Free State EMS have reported three fatalities after a bus collided with a truck on the N1, between Koppies & Kroonstad. Many other people have been injured but figures were not immediately available. 3 Fatalities as Bus collided with a truck on the N1 between Koppies & Kroonstad. https://t.co/oM2hNtokUe  @fs_health  #ArriveAlive pic.twitter.com/H0RkllxNjB â€” Arrive Alive (@_ArriveAlive) November 18, 2017  Meanwhile, a 27-year-old man was killed after he lost control of his motorbike on the N1 just after the Huguenot Tunnel close to Du Toitskloof in the Western Cape yesterday evening. When ER24 paramedics arrived on the scene at approximately 19H20, they found the man lying on the grass between the two barriers. Unfortunately, the man showed no signs of life and he was declared dead at the scene by ER24. The exact details of the incident are not yet known to our paramedics.